body:
Racking up an impressive amount of coverage for their two fantastic debut track, Orlando duo **Saes** have unleashed another beauteous, dream-pop number.

Again utilising the vocal relationship between Jennifer and Michael, _Prom Date_ is part tweet, part gorgeous, synth led loveliness. Check out _Prom Date_ below.
